      "author": "philpalmieri",
      "description": "First public release of Taskgregator.\n\n**Install:** download `main.js`, `manifest.json`, and `styles.css` below into `<vault>/.obsidian/plugins/taskgregator/`, then enable **Taskgregator** in Settings → Community plugins.\n\n### Features\n- Context tree (Projects/People/Areas) with roll-up counts\n- Cross-indexing by `[[wikilink]]`\n- Tag-driven smart lists (Today, Follow-up, Snippet Ideas, Someday)\n- Inline editing: priority, due/start dates, status, tags\n- Per-task detail notes (sidecars)\n- Native right-click menu on task lines across the vault\n- Self-contained: no Dataview/Tasks runtime dependency",
      "downloadCount": 2,
      "draft": false,
      "name": "0.1.0",
